wikipedia_page.main: Moustafa Palazli Chousein-Oglou (Turkish: Mustafa Palazlı Hüseyinoğlu) (born 28 December 1990 in Xanthi, Greece), sometimes known as Moustafa Palazli is a Greek-born British actor of Turkish origin. He is best known for playing Blane in the BBC children's comedy adventure M.I. High.
